Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_inb_chn6

USBN_DMA0_INB_CHN6 = USBN's Inbound DMA for USB0 Channel6

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 writes to L2C via Channel6. Writing of this register sets the base address.
